{
  "texts": [
    "ResultsIn this investigation, a series of experiments were conducted to assess the performance of various deep learning models in detecting pneumonia from chest X-ray images.",
    "The baseline model, ResNet-50, achieved a satisfactory accuracy of 0.94,as show in Fig. 6, demonstrating its effectiveness in this task.",
    "However, to further enhance the model's performance, we incorporated additional components.In the first enhancement, we incorporated skip connections into the ResNet-50 architecture.",
    "Skip connections effectively captured more informative features and facilitated feature interaction.",
    "This led to improved information propagation and feature representation."
  ]
}